<h3 id="15-cleanfox">15. Cleanfox</h3>

<p>Cleanfox is a tool designed to help you declutter your inbox by unsubscribing from unwanted newsletters and deleting old, irrelevant emails. It’s a great way to reduce email clutter and stay focused on the most important communications.</p>

<p><img src="https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/dPGl3_1LhzZIO6KdLA9E51Nbn6nrTE3Nebw7yGLOEuifJ-XH29MvKsR0s8Z-3ode5eZp=w2560-h1440-rw" alt="" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Unsubscribe from unwanted newsletters with a single click.</li>
  <li>Delete old, irrelevant emails to clean up your inbox.</li>
  <li>Track your environmental impact by reducing the number of emails stored on servers.</li>
</ul>

<p><a href="https://www.cleanfox.io/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration: none"> Get Cleanfox <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right"></i></a></p>

